Cell["\<\
To keep track of how many times an eigenvalue appears as a root of the \
characteristic polynomial, we also use the term algebraic multiplicity.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.907423053857176*^9, 
  3.907423088123458*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"45080440-0b55-4292-9882-\
